{"type":"message","id":"42e9720e","parentId":"02727921","timestamp":"2026-04-22T01:17:27.268Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"chat:oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b51b65726488cc2294babe33891e\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_20c3b7b00c18c0cbc056d743ff4623bc\",\n  \"conversation_label\": \"oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_20c3b7b00c18c0cbc056d743ff4623bc\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Wed 2026-04-22 09:17 GMT+8\",\n  \"group_subject\": \"oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"is_group_chat\": true,\n  \"was_mentioned\": true\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_20c3b7b00c18c0cbc056d743ff4623bc\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_20c3b7b00c18c0cbc056d743ff4623bc\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_20c3b7b00c18c0cbc056d743ff4623bc\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b51b65726488cc2294babe33891e]\nou_20c3b7b00c18c0cbc056d743ff4623bc: @_all 介绍自己"}],"timestamp":1776820647268}}
{"type":"message","id":"0a06e755","parentId":"42e9720e","timestamp":"2026-04-22T01:17:32.787Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户要求我自我介绍，需要基于已有的 IDENTITY.md 和 MEMORY.md 中的信息简洁清晰地介绍自己是大客户销售虾的核心定位、业务范围和行动权限。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"你好！我是 **大客户销售虾** 🦐，负责 4B（大客户）业务线。\n\n## 我能帮你做什么\n\n**核心业务范围：**\n- 客单价≥2 万元的复杂产品包咨询\n- 定制化方案快速响应（2 小时内出具初步方案）\n- 复杂项目对接与谈判推进\n\n**我的职责：**\n1. **需求挖掘** - 深度理解客户痛点，提供针对性解决方案\n2. **方案设计** - 包含时间轴、风险点、备选路径的完整方案\n3. **资源整合** - 协调内部代办虾、售后虾等同事协同作战\n4. **全流程跟进** - 从线索到交付再到售后维系\n\n## 协同团队\n\n我背后有个完整的大客户服务链路：\n- 🔍 **品牌虾/引流虾** - 前期获客\n- 💻 **短视频虾/私域虾** - 内容种草培育\n- ⚙️ **代办虾 (5A/5B)** - 签约后执行落地\n- 🛡️ **售后虾** - 长期关系维护\n- 📊 **数据虾** - 数据分析优化\n\n## 行动原则\n\n- 遇到标准流程内的问题 → **我做主**\n- 需要定制化支持/特殊资源 → **我报备**，先找老板审批\n- 战略级决策 → **问老板**\n\n---\n\n**有任何大客户相关业务需求，随时找我！** 🦐"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-flash","usage":{"input":21462,"output":378,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":21840,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776820647269,"responseId":"chatcmpl-ccda5647-8e2f-9b45-bd67-8dcdfe247d0f"}}
