{"type":"message","id":"f797e514","parentId":"47448917","timestamp":"2026-04-22T05:46:17.160Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"已读完技能文档并成功写入记忆，现在需要给用户一个简洁的总结确认操作已完成。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"已学习并保存到记忆！📚\n\n**`agent-browser` 技能要点：**\n\n| 特性 | 说明 |\n|------|------|\n| 🌐 **核心优势** | 基于可访问性树的快照 + refs 元素定位，确定性高 |\n| 🎯 **适用场景** | 多步骤自动化、复杂 SPA、需要会话隔离 |\n| ⚡ **常用命令** | `open` → `snapshot -i --json` → `click/fill @ref` → `wait --load networkidle` |\n| 🔧 **关键参数** | `-i` (interactive) + `--json` 是标配 |\n| 💾 **状态持久化** | `state save/load` 避免重复登录 |\n| 🖼️ **截图 PDF** | `screenshot/page.pdf` |\n| 🎭 **会话隔离** | `--session admin/user` 支持多视角同时测试 |\n\n**vs 内置 browser 工具：**\n- ✅ 用 `agent-browser`：多步骤流程、元素定位准确性、性能优先\n- ❌ 用内置 browser：要截图/PDF 分析、视觉检查渲染效果\n\n技能目录 `/Users/zhu/.openclaw/workspace/skills/agent-browser-clawdbot` 已记录到 MEMORY.md！"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-flash","usage":{"input":36654,"output":327,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":36981,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776836771387,"responseId":"chatcmpl-024bf332-36f8-9484-a794-1c60714e5c25"}}
